---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Wallpapering in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock' description='Professional wallpapering across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:420px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(1).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 30%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 56px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Wallpapering</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Wallpapering</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.5;">Straight drops, matched patterns, tight seams. Feature walls and full rooms done precisely.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The work</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,34px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 24px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Wallpapering is a precision job. The wall has to be right before you start.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">Walls that aren't plumb, surfaces with texture, unprimed new plaster — all create problems once the paper goes on. Seams that lift, drops that aren't quite vertical, pattern repeats that don't align at eye level. These aren't fixable after the fact.</p>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">We prepare the wall surface before hanging — lining paper where required, sizing or primer applied — and hang to a plumb line from the start, not from the corner. Pattern repeats are calculated before cutting so the wastage is managed and the match is where it matters.</p>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Feature walls, chimney breast panels, full-room hanging, paste-the-wall systems, paste-the-paper — all covered. We hang standard and specialist papers including grasscloth and fabric-backed.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a wallpapering quote.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;">Fixed price. Surface prep included in the price.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:28px 0 0;">Cancellations less than 48 hours before booking incur a £100 fee.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
